=Write a comprehensive blog post based on this research:

**Topic:** {{ $json.topic }}

**Angle:** {{ $json.angle }}

**Target Audience:** {{ $json.targetAudience }}

**Research:**
{{ $json.research }}

**Citations/Sources:**
{{ JSON.stringify($json.citations || []) }}

Write a 1500-2000 word blog post in JSON format. Include:
1. An attention-grabbing title
2. A compelling introduction with a hook
3. 3-5 main sections with H2 headings
4. Practical tips or examples
5. A conclusion with a call-to-action
6. Naturally reference sources where relevant

Output JSON with this structure:
{
  "excerpt": "An apt description of the current blog post...",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "id": "block-1705432123457-def456",
      "type": "text",
      "order": 1,
      "content": "This is the introduction paragraph."
    }
  ],
  "version": "1.0"
}

Base the block structure on: {{ JSON.stringify($json.blocks) }}

Use different combinations of blocks to give the page more flare.
Excerpt is plain text.

